note: I work from my home office in Winthrop, a small town in lakes region of central Maine. I studied art at University of Maine at Orono and Goddard College Plainfield Vermont. My art studies were in art history, painting, and photography. For over 25 years I have been involved with computers, software, managing data, databases and doing graphic design. Starting in 2021 I began offering self-publishing assistance and page design to others who want to self-publish using Amazon or Ingram Spark.
